### B-211 — End-to-End Full Hand Flow
###
### 목적 (Foundation.md Ch.5 의존성 사슬 검증):
###   RFID → Engine → CC → BO → (Overlay)
###   1핸드 완주를 단일 시나리오에서 회귀 검증한다.
###
### 단위 시나리오 (10~62) 는 각 계약을 격리 검증하지만,
### "조립" 단계의 회귀 (이벤트 순서, seq monotonic, 팟 정합) 는 본 시나리오만 검출 가능.
###
### Pipeline (4팀 합의 assertion 정의 = B-211 Definition of Done):
###   Setup       — team2 (admin login, deck register, launch CC)
###   WriteGameInfo — team2 + team4 (CC NEW HAND → GameInfoAck)
###   Deal        — team3 (Engine deal 6 cards) + team4 (CC 카드 인식)
###   Preflop     — team4 (CC 6 액션 입력) + team3 (Engine 정합)
###   Flop/Turn/River — team3 (DealCommunity) + team4 (ActionPerformed)
###   Showdown    — team3 (PotAwarded + HandCompleted)
###   Commit      — team2 (BO hand record persistence)
###
### 본 파일은 HTTP request 시나리오만 직렬화한다. WebSocket 단계는 주석 + wscat 명령으로 명시.
###
### Coverage:
###   - CCR-021 (WS seq monotonic + replay)
###   - CCR-024 (WriteGameInfo + GameInfoAck)
###   - CCR-026 (Deck register + CardDetected)
###   - CCR-029 (CC Launch)
###   - CCR-031 (BO reconnect — 회귀 보강)
###   - Foundation.md Ch.5 의존성 사슬 (실시간 출력)
###
### 실행 환경:
###   docker compose --profile e2e up -d (bo, engine, mocks)
###   integration-tests-e2e.yml workflow 가 본 시나리오를 httpyac 로 자동 실행.
###
### 의존:
###   - B-210 (Overlay Rive OutputEvent 매핑) — 본 시나리오에서는 stub 으로 처리.
###     Overlay 단계 assertion 은 "WS 이벤트 발송됨" 까지만 검증, 실제 frame 렌더링은 제외.

@host = http://localhost:18001
@engine_host = http://localhost:18080
@ws_cc = ws://localhost:18001/ws/cc

@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}
@operator_token = {{$dotenv OPERATOR_JWT}}

@test_table_id = 1
@test_event_id = 1
@test_flight_id = 1
@expected_hand_id = 248

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase A: Setup
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### A.1 GET /api/v1/auth/me — Admin 인증 확인 (preflight)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": {
#     "user_id": "...",
#     "email": "admin@ebs.local",
#     "role": "admin"
#   }
# }
#
# Assertion (team2 owns):
#   - status === 200
#   - data.role === "admin"

### A.2 POST /api/v1/decks — 54장 deck 등록 (RFID UID → rank/suit 매핑)
# @name registerDeck
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deck_name": "v99-full-hand-test-deck",
  "cards": [
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1V001", "rank": 12, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1V002", "rank": 11, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1V003", "rank": 10, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1V004", "rank": 9,  "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1V005", "rank": 8,  "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1V006", "rank": 7,  "suit": 0 }
  ]
}

# (실제 실행 시 54장 전체. 시나리오에서는 처음 6장만 필수 — 6-handed 핸드 시작 가능)
#
# 예상: 201 Created
# {
#   "deck_id": "dk_v99...",
#   "card_count": 6,
#   "created_at": "..."
# }
#
# Assertion (team2 owns):
#   - status === 201
#   - data.deck_id matches /^dk_/
#   - card_count === 54  (CI 실제 실행 시. 본 파일은 minimal — 6장만 필수)

### A.3 PATCH /api/v1/tables/{id}/active_deck — deck 할당
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/tables/{{test_table_id}}/active_deck
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deck_id": "{{registerDeck.response.body.deck_id}}"
}

# 예상: 200 OK
# Assertion (team2 owns):
#   - status === 200
#   - data.active_deck_id === registerDeck.deck_id

### A.4 POST /api/v1/tables/{id}/launch-cc — CC 인스턴스 발급
# @name launchCC
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tables/{{test_table_id}}/launch-cc
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

# 예상: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": {
#     "table_id": 1,
#     "status": "live",
#     "cc_instance_id": "cc-uuid-...",
#     "launch_token": "eyJhbGc...",
#     "ws_url": "ws://localhost:18001/ws/cc?table_id=1",
#     "launched_at": "..."
#   }
# }
#
# Assertion (team2 + team4 owns):
#   - status === 200
#   - data.launch_token decode: { sub: cc_instance_id, exp: now+300s, role: "cc_launch", table_id: 1 }
#   - data.ws_url 가 본 _env.http 의 ws_cc 와 일치

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase B: WriteGameInfo (WebSocket — 수동/CI runner manual step)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# CC 가 NEW HAND 버튼 누르면 WriteGameInfo 발행.
# 본 시나리오는 .http 만 직렬화되므로 WS 단계는 명령어 + 예상 응답 으로 기록.
#
# B.1 WS 연결:
#   wscat -c '{{ws_cc}}?table_id=1&token={{launchCC.response.body.data.launch_token}}&cc_instance_id={{launchCC.response.body.data.cc_instance_id}}&format=json'
#
# 예상 수신 (InitialState):
#   { "type": "InitialState", "payload": { "table": {...}, "seats": [...], "current_hand": null } }
#
# Assertion (team4 owns):
#   - type === "InitialState"
#   - current_hand === null  (새 launch 직후)
#
# B.2 WS 송신 (CC → BO/Engine):
#   {
#     "type": "WriteGameInfo",
#     "payload": {
#       "table_id": 1,
#       "hand_id": 248,
#       "dealer_seat": 3,
#       "sb_seat": 4,
#       "bb_seat": 5,
#       "sb_amount": 500,
#       "bb_amount": 1000,
#       "ante_amount": 0,
#       "big_blind_ante": false,
#       "straddle_seats": [],
#       "blind_structure_id": "v99-test-bs",
#       "blind_level": 1,
#       "game_type": "no_limit_holdem",
#       "active_seats": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6],
#       "chip_denominations": [100, 500, 1000, 5000, 25000]
#     },
#     "idempotency_key": "uuid-wgi-248",
#     "source_id": "cc-table-1",
#     "message_id": "msg-wgi-1"
#   }
#
# 예상 수신:
#   { "type": "GameInfoAck", "payload": { "hand_id": 248, "ready_for_deal": true, "seq": <N+1> } }
#
# Assertion (team2 + team4 owns):
#   - type === "GameInfoAck"
#   - ready_for_deal === true
#   - seq 가 InitialState 의 seq + 1

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase C: Deal (RFID 6 cards × seat 1~6)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Mock RFID driver 가 6 card detection 이벤트 발송.
# 실 hardware 없이 mock: POST /api/v1/_mock/rfid/scan 으로 트리거 (CI-only endpoint).

### C.1 POST /api/v1/_mock/rfid/scan — Seat 1 카드 인식 (CI-only)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/_mock/rfid/scan
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_id": 1,
  "uid": "04A3B2C1V001",
  "antenna": "seat_1"
}

# 예상: 202 Accepted
# {
#   "queued": true,
#   "event_id": "...",
#   "expected_ws_event": "CardDetected"
# }
#
# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - status === 202
#   - WS 채널에 CardDetected event 도달 (수동 wscat 검증)
#   - DealCommunity 발생 안 함 (hole card 단계)

### C.2 POST /api/v1/_mock/rfid/scan — Seat 2~6 (반복, 간략 1건만 표기)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/_mock/rfid/scan
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_id": 1,
  "uid": "04A3B2C1V002",
  "antenna": "seat_2"
}

# (Seat 3~6 동일 패턴. CI runner 가 V003~V006 까지 자동 반복.)
#
# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - 6 card 모두 CardDetected event 수신
#   - 전체 seq 단조증가

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase D: Preflop Actions (WS — CC action input)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# CC operator 가 6키 입력 (각 seat 의 action). 본 시나리오는 표준 시퀀스:
#   Seat 6 (UTG): fold
#   Seat 1: fold
#   Seat 2: call 1000
#   Seat 3 (dealer): raise 3000
#   Seat 4 (SB): fold
#   Seat 5 (BB): call 2000 (raise to 3000 - posted 1000)
#
# D.1 WS 송신 (CC → BO) — 반복 6회:
#   {
#     "type": "ActionPerformed",
#     "payload": { "seat_no": 6, "action": "fold" },
#     "idempotency_key": "uuid-act-1",
#     "local_seq": 1
#   }
#   ... (5회 추가, action 다양)
#
# 예상 수신 (BO 가 각 Action 별 broadcast):
#   { "type": "ActionPerformed", "seq": <N>, "payload": { "seat_no": 6, "action": "fold" } }
#
# Assertion (team4 + team3 owns):
#   - 모든 ActionPerformed seq 단조증가
#   - 마지막 Action 처리 후 betting_round closed → Engine 이 DealCommunity (flop 3장) 자동 발송
#   - 폴드 seat 은 이후 round 에서 액션 요구되지 않음

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase E: Flop (Engine DealCommunity 3 cards)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Mock RFID 가 flop 3장 발송 → Engine DealCommunity event 발생.

### E.1 POST /api/v1/_mock/rfid/scan — Flop 카드 1 (community)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/_mock/rfid/scan
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_id": 1,
  "uid": "04A3B2C1V010",
  "antenna": "community_1"
}

# (community_2, community_3 반복. 총 3장 인식.)
#
# 예상 WS broadcast:
#   { "type": "DealCommunity", "seq": <N>, "payload": { "street": "flop", "cards": ["Ah", "Kd", "Qs"] } }
#
# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - DealCommunity event 1회 발생
#   - cards.length === 3
#   - street === "flop"

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase F: Flop Actions (WS — 동일 패턴, 줄여 표기)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Action 시퀀스 (예시):
#   Seat 2: check
#   Seat 3: bet 2000
#   Seat 5: call 2000
#   Seat 2: fold
#
# 예상 결과: 2 active seats (3, 5) → turn 진입

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase G: Turn (1 card)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# G.1 Mock RFID — turn community
# (E.1 동일 패턴, uid V013, antenna community_4)
#
# 예상 WS:
#   { "type": "DealCommunity", "payload": { "street": "turn", "cards": ["Js"] } }
#
# Turn actions: seat 3 check, seat 5 check → river

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase H: River (1 card)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# H.1 Mock RFID — river community
# 예상 WS: { "type": "DealCommunity", "payload": { "street": "river", "cards": ["Td"] } }
#
# River actions: seat 3 bet 5000, seat 5 call → showdown

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase I: Showdown + Pot Award
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Engine 이 모든 자동 처리. CC operator 입력 불필요.
#
# 예상 WS 시퀀스 (Engine 발송):
#   1. { "type": "Showdown", "payload": { "winners": [3], "hands": {...} } }
#   2. { "type": "PotAwarded", "payload": { "awards": [{ "seat_no": 3, "amount": 14000 }] } }
#   3. { "type": "HandCompleted", "payload": { "hand_number": 248 } }
#
# Assertion (team3 owns):
#   - 정확히 1 PotAwarded
#   - awards 의 amount 합 === 총 베팅액 (preflop + flop + turn + river)
#   - HandCompleted hand_number === 248 (WriteGameInfo 의 hand_id)
#   - 모든 이벤트 seq 단조증가

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase J: BO Commit Verification (HTTP — 자동화 가능)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### J.1 GET /api/v1/hands/248 — 핸드 기록 영속화 확인
GET {{host}}/api/v1/hands/{{expected_hand_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK
# {
#   "data": {
#     "hand_id": 248,
#     "table_id": 1,
#     "status": "completed",
#     "winner_seats": [3],
#     "total_pot": 14000,
#     "actions_count": 12,
#     "community_cards": ["Ah", "Kd", "Qs", "Js", "Td"],
#     "started_at": "...",
#     "completed_at": "..."
#   }
# }
#
# Assertion (team2 owns):
#   - status === 200
#   - data.status === "completed"
#   - data.winner_seats.length >= 1
#   - data.total_pot > 0
#   - data.community_cards.length === 5

### J.2 GET /api/v1/events/replay?from_seq=0&channel=cc_event — 전체 이벤트 회수
GET {{host}}/api/v1/events/replay?from_seq=0&channel=cc_event&hand_id={{expected_hand_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 OK
# {
#   "events": [
#     { "seq": 1, "type": "InitialState", ... },
#     { "seq": 2, "type": "GameInfoAck", ... },
#     ...
#     { "seq": N, "type": "HandCompleted", ... }
#   ]
# }
#
# Assertion (team2 + team4 owns — CCR-021 regression):
#   - events[].seq 가 strictly monotonic increasing (gap 0)
#   - 마지막 event.type === "HandCompleted"
#   - 첫 event.type === "InitialState" 또는 "GameInfoAck"
#   - "PotAwarded" 정확히 1회 등장

### J.3 GET /api/v1/_mock/overlay/last-frame — Overlay 출력 stub 검증 (선택)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/_mock/overlay/last-frame?table_id={{test_table_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 본 endpoint 는 B-210 (Overlay Rive OutputEvent 매핑) 완료 후 활성.
# 현재 stub 응답:
# {
#   "implemented": false,
#   "todo": "B-210 — Overlay Rive frame extraction"
# }
#
# Assertion (conductor owns):
#   - B-210 완료 시: data.frame_data 가 base64 png + last_event.type === "HandCompleted"
#   - 현재 (stub): implemented === false 인 경우만 허용 (회귀 시 false → true 전환 검출)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
